codeText: protected JsonEncoding getJsonEncoding(@Nullable MimeType mimeType) {_		if (mimeType != null && mimeType.getCharset() != null) {_			Charset charset = mimeType.getCharset()__			for (JsonEncoding encoding : JsonEncoding.values()) {_				if (charset.name().equals(encoding.getJavaName())) {_					return encoding__				}_			}_		}_		return JsonEncoding.UTF8__	}
